room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by Escape Plan Georgia in Atlanta
room_address: 3735 Harrison Road SW, Suite 600, Loganville, GA 30052
room_description:
The year is 1964. You hear strange noises and strange lights have been spotted over Roswell, New Mexico. Increased military activity is seen everywhere. The rumors are spreading… “They’ve found aliens.”
Your group has infiltrated “Area 51,’ the top-secret military headquarters. Now that you’re in, can you solve the mystery that is Area 51?
